CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,7,Fstarted an investigation after a
OL,8,Frobbery in the car park of John Lewis
OL,9,Fin Cheadle, when a man reportedly
OL,10,Fthreatened to stab a woman with a
OL,11,Fscrewdriver if she did not give him
OL,12,Fher watch and engagement ring, worth
OL,13,Fnearly #200,000 combined.
OL,15,FOfficers were able to track the mans
OL,16,Fcar using CCTV, and investigations
OL,17,Ffound that the victim had been
OL,18,Ffollowed using a tracker prior to the
OL,19,Frobbery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,FJunior Owen, James Melia and Anthony
OL,7,FWatson were later arrested, and a
OL,8,Ftracker, watches and drugs were seized
OL,9,Ffrom their addresses.
OL,11,FFollowing their arrests for the
OL,12,FCheadle robbery, officers discovered
OL,13,Fthat they had committed further crimes
OL,14,Ftargeting high-valued goods across a
OL,15,Fseries burglaries across Cheshire and
OL,16,FGreater Manchester.
OL,18,FIn total, the men were linked to eight
OL,19,Fcrimes starting in 2021, with most
OL,20,Fhappening in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,FPolice found messages between the trio
OL,7,Fwhere they would plan the robberies in
OL,8,Fdetail; how they followed the victims,
OL,9,Fhow they would rob them and research
OL,10,Finto sites to sell the stolen goods.
OL,12,FThe men threatened women for their
OL,13,Fjewellery in their homes, with one
OL,14,Fheld at knifepoint while another was
OL,15,Fheld by her hair and forced to take
OL,16,Foff her wedding rings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,FOn another occasion the men stole 10
OL,7,Fwatches with a total value of
OL,8,Fapproximately #50,000, while in
OL,9,Fanother they targeted a business
OL,10,Fselling designer goods in Altrincham,
OL,11,Fand handbags worth #200,000 were
OL,12,Fstolen.
OL,14,FA further crime included the robbery
OL,15,Fof a vape store in Stockport, with the
OL,16,Fvarious vaping goods being stuffed in
OL,17,Fa duvet bag. Around #5,000 was also
OL,18,Ftaken during the incident in January
OL,19,F2023, with the stolen vapes later
OL,20,Fbeing advertised for sale.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,FAnother robbery in Stockport in
OL,7,FJanuary 2023 saw goods with a retail
OL,8,Fvalue of #300,000 taken from a store,
OL,9,Fafter the worker was threatened. The
OL,10,FCCTV was ripped out before the
OL,11,Foffender left through the rear doors.
OL,13,FDetective Constable Lucy Williams
OL,14,Fsaid: "These three criminals made a
OL,15,Fliving out of violently stealing other
OL,16,Fpeople's hard-earned belongings, being
OL,17,Fmotivated by personal gain and not
OL,18,Fcaring for who they threatened.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,F"This was a complex and comprehensive
OL,7,Finvestigation, which saw extensive
OL,8,Fphone and data analysis, mapping out
OL,9,Fthe three criminals and linking them
OL,10,Fto their offences. I want to pay
OL,11,Ftribute to the officers with
OL,12,FStockport's Neighbourhood Crime Team
OL,13,Fwho have dedicated so many hours to
OL,14,Fhelp get today's results.
OL,16,F"Their crimes left people terrified
OL,17,Ffor their own lives and unsafe in
OL,18,Ftheir own homes, and I am glad they
OL,19,Fare now behind bars for their actions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779872682
OL,3,CGang members jailed after #1m worth
OL,4,Cgoods stolen
OL,6,F"I hope that their victims can feel
OL,7,Fsome comfort at today's result ` we
OL,8,Ftake reports of robberies and
OL,9,Fburglaries incredibly seriously and
OL,10,Fwill do our utmost best to find those
OL,11,Fresponsible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
